titles.title: Making further continuing appropriations for the fiscal year 1994, and for other purposes.

action.text: Rules Committee Resolution H. Res. 304 Reported to House. Rule provides for consideration of H.J. Res. 288 with 1 hour of general debate. Previous question shall be considered as ordered without intervening motions except motion to recommit. Providing for consideration of the resolution in the House.
Referred to the House Committee on Appropriations.

bill.summary: 11/9/1993--Introduced. Extends the law making further continuing appropriations for FY 1994.
